deck: Artist of Crouching tiger hidden Dragon, He has also worked on the comic adaption of Shalolin Soccer and many other titles
description: Andy Seto taught him self how to draw from a young age, mixing both manga and western art. in 1983 Seto worked on several titles and then in 1990 started working for the freeman label. He focused more on his manga art work from here on out and began finding his own personal style. In 1993 he began work on Cyber Weapon Z with Chris lau and foused on a goup of teenagers practicing martial arts, this would later be adpeted into a animated series. Seto would also go on to do the art work for the Crouching Tiger Hidden Dragon series and a few other film to comic adaptions including Shalolin Soccer.
name: Andy Seto
